title: [Bloodriven Bowery, Back]
description: The back room is cluttered with various shipping crates partially concealed with stained canvas tarps.  A small area has been cleared out to display a set of rickety shelves and a warped pine rack.

The back room is cluttered with various shipping crates partially concealed with stained canvas tarps.  A small area has been cleared out to display a set of rickety shelves and a warped pine rack which has a dark leather sack hanging on one side.
